eetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/light-of-day.jpg?fit=1080%2C1080&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 32613, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/03/06/roll-of-the-dice-mansion-on-the-hill/", "url_meta": {"origin": 35903, "position": 2}, "title": "Roll of the Dice: Mansion on the Hill", "author": "Ken", "date": "March 6, 2022", "format": false, "excerpt": "How a tale of 19th-century heartbreak and a 1947 Hank Williams song led to one of the most affecting tracks on Nebraska.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Roll of the Dice&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Roll of the Dice", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/roll-of-the-dice/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mansion.jpg?fit=1200%2C743&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mansion.jpg?fit=1200%2C743&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mansion.jpg?fit=1200%2C743&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mansion.jpg?fit=1200%2C743&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/mansion.jpg?fit=1200%2C743&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 13703, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/10/10/cover-me-bettye-lavette-streets-of-philadelphia/", "url_meta": {"origin": 35903, "position": 3}, "title": "Cover Me, Bettye LaVette: Streets of Philadelphia", "author": "Ken", "date": "October 10, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "What can possibly be more powerful than Bettye LaVette's 2007 cover of \"Streets of Philadelphia?\" A live performance from a decade later. Both are required listening.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/song-of-america.jpg?fit=500%2C500&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200}, "classes": []}, {"id": 59693, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/20/kingdom-of-days-september-20-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 35903, "position": 4}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: September 20", "author": "Ken", "date": "September 20, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce releases Nebraska, films the video for \"Lonesome Day\" and photobombs a couple's engagement photos. Plus, Patti appears solo on Letterman, the live debut of \"County Fair,\" the first full-album show on the 2009 tour, and more. Whew! Lots of highlights today...", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nebraska.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nebraska.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nebraska.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 55239, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2024/12/06/kingdom-of-days-december-6/", "url_meta": {"origin": 35903, "position": 5}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: December 6", "author": "Ken", "date": "December 6, 2024", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce films the video for \"Streets of Philadelphia,\" Sam Moore makes an E Street cameo, and the Asbury Park holiday shows are in full swing. These and more highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "